I wanna show this great, old Oriental rug
that I found at an estate sale, recently.

00:00:13.960 --> 00:00:20.130
It was marked $2,000, and I got it for, I'm
embarrassed to say, $400.

00:00:20.130 --> 00:00:21.631
And I just love the colors in it.

00:00:21.631 --> 00:00:26.779
And I debated whether to get it or not because
I wasn't sure about the size and there was

00:00:26.779 --> 00:00:27.779
a hole in it.

