Now if you find a rug like this, there are
a couple things you'll wanna keep in mind:

00:01:41.730 --> 00:01:47.230
Since I was able to buy this at such a great
price, I have enough room in my budget, if

00:01:47.230 --> 00:01:49.910
you will, to have this rug cleaned.

00:01:49.910 --> 00:01:52.050
